name: CPL
description: Coupling is a graph based on Web3.0 technology to build a full industry chain transaction. Coupling has introduced a digital ecological transformation model to help traditional supply chain enterprises achieve digital transformation, improve their competitiveness and efficiency. Its digital finance and new supply chain markets have made important innovations, injecting more vitality and innovation into the future supply chain ecosystem. Coupling is a revolutionary industrial chain trading system that utilizes Web3.0 technology to provide safer, more efficient, and low-cost trading and financing services for supply chain participants. At the same time, it helps traditional supply chain enterprises achieve digital transformation, improve enterprise efficiency and competitiveness! Coupling assists in the digital transformation of enterprises, and transaction graphs are born from applications. By integrating WEB3.0 technology, finance, and applications, we have entered a true era of large-scale commercial use!
